# Learn Blazor

## Introduction

This repository contains the source code for [learn-blazor.com](https://learn-blazor.com/).

## Building and Running

This page is built with [Hugo](https://gohugo.io/). If you want to build and/or run it, [install Hugo](https://gohugo.io/getting-started/installing/).

This page uses the [Hugo Learn Theme](https://learn.netlify.com/en/). [Install this theme](https://learn.netlify.com/en/basics/installation/#install-the-theme) into the *themes* folder.

Once you have cared for these prerequisites, you can run the site with `hugo server` and build it with `hugo`.
